OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTruss's tax cuts clearly   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwrong approach - Shapps    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Liz Truss's radical tax-cutting plan   
OL,6, was "clearly" not the right approach,  
OL,7, according to Grant Shapps, who briefly 
OL,8, served in her short-lived government.  
OL,10,FIn a return to the political fray, Ms  
OL,11,FTruss wrote in the Sunday Telegraph    
OL,12,Fthat her economic agenda was never     
OL,13,Fgiven a "realistic chance".            
OL,15,FBusiness Secretary Mr Shapps said he   
OL,16,Fagreed with Ms Truss on wanting lower  
OL,17,Ftaxes - but inflation must fall first. 
OL,19,F"You can't just go straight to those   
OL,20,Ftax cuts," he said.                    
